name: mbe im cat
description:
And I'm an artist, t00. 

Many influences: This meme of an individual joining a zoom court hearing with a cat filter on and not sure how to turn it off... which my clients of all ages laughed about together as we were toggling and playing around with filters. But also gm coffee at nft.nyc where legendary crypto artist Coldie told his story of supporting kitty bungalow's and feeling it when he said that we're all cats. And generally just having fun making gifs these days as a way to make and spread messages.
